casebody.data:
PEOPLE
v.
SINGH S244552 Supreme Court of California DECEMBER 13, 2017 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The request to supplement the petition for review is granted. The petition for review is **12*328granted. The matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Third Appellate District, with directions to vacate its decision and reconsider the cause in light of S.B. 620 (Stats. 2017, ch. 682). ( Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
